node.text:
Our ‘Dusty Blue Floral Thread Embroidered Lehenga’ from our upcoming "Amour" collection is a reminiscent of blooming chrysanthemums under a clear blue sky on a beautiful summer day. The cropped sleeveless choli features silver laces of gota and foil laid geometrically against a solid light blue backdrop. The lehenga has been accentuated with a jaal of delicate and elaborate floral motifs in shades of pink and blue. The hem has been rendered using the same silver laces of the choli, making the whole look aesthetically coordinated. The net dupatta has been worked with a spray of small floral motifs, neatly finished with a laced border.

Price: $195 USD | Launching August 28th at 10 AM PST, exclusively at Lashkaraa.com

node.text:
To our customers worldwide: 

In an effort to provide our customers with more frequent new launches, all new launches effective August 18, 2021 will not be restocked once sold out. Since the launch of our brand, we have always restocked our items online, usually on a monthly basis, to assure we can keep items in stock for months at a time. Doing so, however, limits our capacity to launch and produce new designs in a timely fashion. We are making this change so we can focus on providing our customers with more new designs on a monthly basis. 

We will share previews of all new designs launched henceforth with pricing so you may see if any style is to your liking prior to the launch date. Plus sizes will also be available to purchase the same day for new launches so customers will not need to wait to place a custom order for the same. If any style is to your liking, we encourage you to purchase on the launch date to avoid disappointment. 

We thank you in advance as we navigate these changes and are excited to share with you the many new things we have been working on. 

With love,
Team Lashkaraa

Our Coral Pink and Off White Gharara Suit has been painstakingly curated against a coral pink net canvas with a silverish sheen to it. The element that stand out the most on the shirt is the hem which features tracery frameworks carrying a floral vase inside. The neatly worked neckline and  a generous spray of bootis on the daman adds a spring-like subtlety. The outfit has been paired with an embroidered gharara and a tulle dupatta with elaborate embellishments and finished with a silver gota lace.
